<h1 id="tax-depreciation" sourcefile="AC-SK/ac-sk-tax-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="14">Tax depreciation</h1>

<p sourcefile="AC-SK/ac-sk-tax-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="16">According to the Income Tax Act No. 595/2003 Coll., a taxpayer may apply annual depreciation in the first year of depreciation only in an amount corresponding to the number of calendar months in which the property was used to secure income.</p>
<h2 id="depreciation-reduction-setting-in-the-1st-year" sourcefile="AC-SK/ac-sk-tax-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="18">Depreciation reduction setting in the 1st year</h2>
<ol sourcefile="AC-SK/ac-sk-tax-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="20">
<li sourcefile="AC-SK/ac-sk-tax-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="20">Choose the <img src="media/ui-search/search_small.png" sourcefile="AC-SK/ac-sk-tax-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="20" alt="Lightbulb that opens the Tell Me feature." title="Tell me what you want to do">, icon, enter <strong sourcefile="AC-SK/ac-sk-tax-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="20">Fixed Asset Setup</strong> and then choose the related link.</li>
<li sourcefile="AC-SK/ac-sk-tax-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="21">Check the box <strong sourcefile="AC-SK/ac-sk-tax-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="21">Depreciation Reduction First Year</strong>.</li>
<li sourcefile="AC-SK/ac-sk-tax-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="22">Confirm with <strong sourcefile="AC-SK/ac-sk-tax-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="22">OK</strong>.</li>
</ol>
<h2 id="calculation-of-depreciation" sourcefile="AC-SK/ac-sk-tax-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="24">Calculation of depreciation</h2>
<ol sourcefile="AC-SK/ac-sk-tax-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="26">
<li sourcefile="AC-SK/ac-sk-tax-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="26">Choose the <img src="media/ui-search/search_small.png" sourcefile="AC-SK/ac-sk-tax-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="26" alt="Lightbulb that opens the Tell Me feature." title="Tell me what you want to do">, icon, enter <strong sourcefile="AC-SK/ac-sk-tax-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="26">SK Calculate Depreciation</strong> and then choose the related link.</li>
<li sourcefile="AC-SK/ac-sk-tax-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="27">In the fields of the window that appears, enter the parameters for depreciation.
Do not activate the <strong sourcefile="AC-SK/ac-sk-tax-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="28">Use Force No. of Days</strong> field, and do not enter a value in the <strong sourcefile="AC-SK/ac-sk-tax-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="28">Force No. of Days</strong>.</li>
<li sourcefile="AC-SK/ac-sk-tax-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="29">Confirm with <strong sourcefile="AC-SK/ac-sk-tax-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="29">OK</strong>.</li>
</ol>
<div class="NOTE" sourcefile="AC-SK/ac-sk-tax-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="31">
<h5>Note</h5>
<p sourcefile="AC-SK/ac-sk-tax-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="32">On the <strong sourcefile="AC-SK/ac-sk-tax-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="32">FA card</strong> in tax <strong sourcefile="AC-SK/ac-sk-tax-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="32">FA Depreciation Books</strong> enter the first day of the month in the <strong sourcefile="AC-SK/ac-sk-tax-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="32">Starting date of depreciation</strong> field.</p>
</div>
